HEADWORD: Flighter
<hw>Flight"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Brewing)</fld>
<def>A horizontal vane revolving over the surface of wort in a cooler,
to produce a circular current in the liquor.</def>
